aboutBody1: Leqahy is a platform which provides poultrymen with everything they need regarding poultry, without having to leave their farm or warehouse.
aboutBody2:
Poultrymen can order poultry vaccines, antibiotics, disinfectants, growth stimulators and more through our application and they’ll be delivered right to their door. 
 Poultrymen can also order any type of poultry feed and different types of chicks from the company they desire and Leqahy will provide them with door-to-door delivery.
aboutBody3:
Leqahy offers in-lab vaccinations where poultrymen can choose the vaccine they’d like through our app and our professional vaccination team will head to any destination straight away and vaccinate their chicks. 
 Leqahy gives poultrymen the freedom to make reservations with any of Egypt’s most skillful doctors for consultations regarding poultry and for carrying out lab tests with exclusive offers only through Leqahy.
 Leqahy updates stock market prices day by day, helping poultrymen know the exact prices of chicks, poultry meat, poultry feed and eggs throughout different companies. 
 Leqahy contains a unique learning academy which has recent researches and articles written and done by the most qualified veterinarians in Egypt and across the world.
 If you’re a veterinarian or an agricultural engineer, Leqahy wil help you find the job that suits you through Wuzzuf-Betary.
